Installation instructions:

1. To install sdl library:
	sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev

2. To install image library of SDL:
	sudo apt-get install libsdl2-image-dev

3. To install mixer library of SDL:
	sudo apt-get install libsdl2-mixer-dev

4. To install font support library of SDL:
	sudo apt-get install libsdl2-ttf-dev

Linker flags:
	-lSDL2 -lSDL2_image -lSDL2_mixer -g `sdl2-config --cflags --libs` -lSDL2_ttf

References and Acknowledgment:

1. https://lazyfoo.net/tutorials/SDL/index.php

2. https://www.bogotobogo.com/cplusplus/sockets_server_client.php

3. https://www.linuxhowtos.org/C_C++/socket.htm?userrate=2
